<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terms, Privacy, and Disclaimer</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #000; padding: 60px 80px; background: white; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 3px solid #000; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        .document-title { font-size: 22pt; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .date { text-align: right; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #555; }
        .info-box { background: #f8f8f8; border: 2px solid #333; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .info-box h3 { margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 5px; }
        .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .info-label { font-weight: bold; width: 200px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .info-value { flex: 1; }
        .section { margin: 25px 0; }
        .section-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .section-content { text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        ul { margin-left: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        li { margin-bottom: 5px; }
        strong { font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header"><div class="document-title">TERMS, PRIVACY & DISCLAIMER</div></div>
    <div class="date">Last Updated: {{date}}</div>
    <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Business Information</h3>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Business:</div><div class="info-value">{{BusinessName}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Website:</div><div class="info-value">{{Website}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Contact:</div><div class="info-value">{{Email}}</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content">
            This document combines Terms of Use, Privacy Overview, and Disclaimers for <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong>. By using our website or services, you agree to these terms.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">PART 1: TERMS OF USE</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">1. ACCEPTANCE OF TERMS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            By accessing {{Website}} or using our services, you agree to these Terms. If you disagree, discontinue use immediately.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">2. USE OF WEBSITE</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            You may use our website for lawful purposes only. Prohibited activities include: hacking, distributing malware, scraping content, impersonating others, or violating intellectual property rights.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">3. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            All content on this website is owned by <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> and protected by copyright law. You may not reproduce, distribute, or use our content without permission. <strong>No AI training permitted.</strong>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">4. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> is not liable for damages arising from use of our website or services. Content is provided "as is" without warranties.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">PART 2: PRIVACY OVERVIEW</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">5. DATA COLLECTION</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            We collect personal information (name, email, payment details) and usage data (IP address, cookies, analytics). We use this data to provide services, process payments, send communications, and improve user experience.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">6. DATA SHARING</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            We do not sell your data. We share with service providers (payment processors, email tools, analytics) and when required by law.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">7. YOUR RIGHTS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            You may request access, correction, or deletion of your data by contacting {{Email}}. You can opt out of marketing emails anytime.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">8. COOKIES</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            We use cookies for functionality, analytics, and advertising. Manage cookies through your browser settings. See our Cookie Policy for details.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">PART 3: DISCLAIMERS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">9. NO PROFESSIONAL ADVICE</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Content on this website is for informational purposes only and does not constitute medical, legal, or financial advice. Consult qualified professionals before making decisions.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">10. HEALTH AND FITNESS DISCLAIMER</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Participation in physical activities involves risk. Consult a physician before starting any fitness program. <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> is not liable for injuries.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">11. RESULTS NOT GUARANTEED</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Testimonials reflect individual experiences and are not guarantees of results. Your results may vary based on effort, consistency, and personal circumstances.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">12. THIRD-PARTY LINKS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            We are not responsible for third-party websites, products, or services linked from our website.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">13. CHANGES TO THIS DOCUMENT</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            We may update these Terms, Privacy Overview, and Disclaimers at any time. Continued use constitutes acceptance of changes.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">14. GOVERNING LAW</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            This document is governed by the laws of <strong>{{Jurisdiction}}</strong>.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">15. CONTACT</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Questions? Contact us at {{Email}} or {{Phone}}.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>